{"tid":1258401,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"同朋友嘈fb藍絲撐警撐修例人嘅心態","createTime":"2019-06-26T05:49:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-26T09:59:52.000Z","uid":141419,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e3df9541cd0fc9e9bb9f6e195c708a1ac426da33","tid":1258401,"uid":141419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T05:49:47.000Z","msg":"哩幾日開番fb睇<br />\n見好多親戚朋友都喺撐修例撐警<br />\n再留意番撐修例、藍絲、撐警、中立偏左嘅言論<br />\n<br />\n大多數都喺圍繞<br />\n冇犯罪怕咩俾人拉<br />\n警察都喺人，唔喺班暴徒飛磚洗開槍？<br />\n搞還搞，阻到人搵食就錯！<br />\n<br />\n我歸納哩堆人喺<br />\n自私底<br />\n心態：各家自掃門前雪<br />\n搵食緊要過一切<br />\n邊度有著數痴邊度<br />\n牆頭草<br />\n港共黑警有黑材料唔&lsquo;敢&rsquo;提<br />\n只要開岩價佢地喺可以冇底線唔諗人格<br />\n<br />\n（先不論佢地有冇俾人洗腦誤導）<br />\n<br />\n我同朋友傾起，意見兩立<br />\n睇下連登各位點睇以上歸納<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />讚成<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />反對"},{"pid":"4f1a498e61e5f085988db71416c1b2430eef30c4","tid":1258401,"uid":141419,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T05:50:55.000Z","msg":"認為講法<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不偏頗<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />偏頗"},{"pid":"fda223981cc8589b86d7a6cb7d27be30b04272c5","tid":1258401,"uid":49918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T05:51:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4faacc500d66a874f51141cbae4ad8ce909b2857","tid":1258401,"uid":141419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fda223981cc8589b86d7a6cb7d27be30b04272c5","tid":1258401,"uid":49918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T05:51:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T05:54:38.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇下佢地睇完有咩偉論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34f996b53ae00d91f5e145bf09c09383a090840d","tid":1258401,"uid":261332,"like":3,"dislike":